 
guild_leaving

7-2-96 
Bp


This will clear the guild status of a player completely:

fix_guild(str) {
  object fool;
   int hh,jj;
   fool = find_player(str);
   jj=0-fool->query_guild_exp();
   call_other(fool,"add_guild_exp",jj);
   hh=0-fool->query_guild_rank();
   fool->add_guild_rank(hh);
   fool->set_guild_name(0);
   fool->set_guild_file(0);
  return 1;
}


Remember a player MUST loose at least 1/6 of their exp when leaving a 
guild

